{"tid":759139,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"不要同兔仔洗澡! 好危險!!!","createTime":"2018-07-28T10:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T11:05:59.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d2e20fe5ba1b2f3e341d027bf23213abb2b4d406","tid":759139,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T10:42:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">兔仔很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險的，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發死。但是，有一個例外：就是如果牠們有poopy butthole, 可以給牠們一個butt bath, 但不要用手直接拉牠們的糞便，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到牠們的肛門和腳然後就可以慢慢清理。兔仔是被捕獵的動物，在大自然內是每個捕獵者的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，但牠們勝於速度, 跑得快。牠們是脆弱的動物，很容易受驚的。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 關於洗澡危險 和怎樣給牠們butt bath:</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F16NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=59988325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">關於兔子身體語言(害怕、開心、憂愁、憤怒）：</span><a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F16NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=f412981f\" target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"960b4a8d571eae3d6ae89f593bc271a206e9e4f3","tid":759139,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T11:05:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領養兔仔，不要買🐰🐰<br />\n<br />\n實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會領養，這裏有太多兔子正在等新主人帶牠們去新的家，過新的生活。詳情可去</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=d8xljKYk2UWvEYkcFoS%2F16NGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=63d95a54\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a> </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子親吻主人，這是代表你是一個好主人，以下2個videos 可看到：</span>